-- Author Lionel Vairon Concerned About 'China Bashing' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-24T11:22:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-24/author-lionel-vairon-concerned-about-china-bashing-audio-.html
Dr. Lionel Vairon, author of "China 
Threat? The Challenges, Myths and Realities of China's Rise," 
says the west often engages in a "China-bashing campaign." 
Vairon talked with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on 
Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock" on July 23rd.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:57
 